{"type": "article", "id": 19068, "title": "行星玻璃杯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-15T09:27:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115146hry0Avql64kzMjHK.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一组非常绚丽的玻璃杯，将《星际大战》中的行星图案印到了上面，一共 6 个，包括 4个行星、月球和死星。每个杯子都呈现出复杂细密的纹路，依托着球形的杯体，让杯子本身成为一个小的星球，是收藏癖的专爱。另有太阳系各星球图案，每个售价 50 美元，<a href=\"http://www.thinkgeek.com/product/irkr/?cpg=cj&amp;ref=&amp;CJURL=&amp;AID=10746449&amp;PID=7817402&amp;SID=skim82526X1534134Xa5e6db398f4de21aca27ca7867f240f9&amp;CJID=2617611\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261457417jockMYgRpm8TNIv.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"542\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.90333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145743N9UiOLQjMbZuSVlr.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"485\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145743oIh1vPpa2w3NS4nK.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145744FXLi6erYV2WImvTA.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}